---
// AuthorBio.astro — Human author box
---

<div class="author-bio">
  <div class="author-bio-avatar">JK</div>
  <div class="author-bio-content">
    <strong class="author-bio-name">James Kim</strong>
    <p class="author-bio-credentials">Finance nerd. Spreadsheet addict. Building free tools since 2024.</p>
    <p class="author-bio-desc">I started ToolCalcs after getting frustrated with calculator sites that wanted my email before showing me a simple mortgage payment. I built the tools I wanted to use myself, then wrote the guides I wished existed when I was figuring out my own finances. I'm not a certified financial advisor — I'm a software developer who reads too many IRS publications. When the numbers matter (taxes, retirement, insurance), I cross-check against official sources and note them in the article. For everything else, I write from experience. <a href="/about/">More about me →</a></p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .author-bio {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 18px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }
  .author-bio-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .author-bio-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .author-bio-name {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .author-bio-credentials {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .author-bio-desc {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .author-bio-desc a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>
